"<command>ssh</command> <option>-L 11000:127.0.0.1:110 user@host</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: faq.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Modify your &kmail; configuration to fetch the mail via POP3 from "
"<userinput>localhost</userinput> and ssh will tunnel the connection for you."
msgstr ""
"&kmail;の設定を変更して<userinput>localhost</userinput>からPOP3によりメールを"
